data.description: Darling house with an amazing fenced-in backyard! This turnkey home has hardwood floors throughout and new carpeting in the den. Cutest mid-mod bathroom with lovely wallpaper! Newer windows throughout and almost all light fixtures have been updated. One car attached garage that has been used as a  workshop. Washer and dryer hookups can be moved to the den to use the garage for parking a car. The sun kissed den provides access to the huge flat yard through a deck. Great outdoor space for your fur babies, human babies, relaxing and entertaining! 7 minutes to the airport, 10 minutes to downtown and 15 minutes to Vanderbilt and Green Hills.
